gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

My Lord of Dharma, speak my words, don't commit sin without reward; 
Don't join the party of those who are going to return empty-handed, that you may not give away your gift to others in vain.

Here is the translation:

He will say the first mantra to him, and then he will take it away; 
He will perform this mantra daily, and a great lord will grant it to you.

Here is the translation:

This is decided by faith, when the world is considered false; 
Guru has written a scripture as he pleased, Ramanuja reads it daily.

Here is the translation:

"Speak, loving husband, listen; grief did not stay in my house, nor did it leave; 
You know everything, every means; if you resist, there will be no fight anywhere."

It did not forget the sorrow, nor did it remember the pain a lot; 
Therefore it wrote happiness and sorrow that is true, 
Does not change even for one moment.

I will do it as you asked. Here is the translation:

I will make it happen just like happiness, now many days unhappiness will be; 
This is the advice given by the faith, I say understand that secret.
